HEADWORD: Harmel
<hw>Har"mel</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧r"m⟦ecr⟧l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar.
<ets>harmal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind of rue
(<spn>Ruta sylvestris</spn>) growing in India. At Lahore the seeds are
used medicinally and for fumigation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

